        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[使用Replit平台免费搭建GitHub下载反代]]></title>
            <link>https://blog.mnxy.eu.org/posts/tech/ghproxy</link>
            <guid>https://blog.mnxy.eu.org/posts/tech/ghproxy</guid>
            <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 05:20:15 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>该教程使用到了<code>Replit</code>平台<code>Education</code>账号，普通账号流量限制10G</p>
</blockquote>
